DATA
----
Figures are derived from the Encuesta Permanente de Hogares (EPH), INDEC
(Argentina) — public "base usuaria" microdata. Only aggregate/derived statistics
are redistributed here, with attribution, consistent with INDEC's terms and the
secreto estadístico (Ley 17.622). Individual records are never shipped — only
aggregates.

The cost-of-living reference layer cites its own external sources inline in
pipeline/config.py.

